   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>In my opinion, the place is so huge with many people.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-b" mid="7" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Good place to run a business, though.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Aren't you afraid of monsters?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You must be happy to have many chances to show off your skills.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Lots of adventurers flock into this city. Thanks to them, the forge business is well managed. Plus, the rumor that massive monsters appearing in Foothills of Black Mountain is spreading, so a lot more people would rush in.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Why are you so pessimistic, young man! At your age, you should interact with various people around the world. This makes you to grow up.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Yes, the most important for a business is location! It's important to find a good location to open shop.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>
I am not afraid of anything except what I can see infront of me. It's not as if the Black Dragon will appear in Foothills of Black Mountain again. Why am I afraid of such monsters?! Besides, the town wall here is very solid.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>
Sure, I'm very glad to have more chances to show my artistic skills. Come and find me whenever you want to see my fantastic and elegant skill.</html>]]></talk_question>
